.Va expandargv
as desired, however.
MTA arguments can always (or also) be specified via the option
.Va sendmail-arguments
\(en please see the description of
.Va sendmail
for more on our interaction with MTAs.
MTA arguments are ignored when mail is send via SMTP data transfer.
